title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
OB: While on the query result page, no data is returned. The expected behavior is that the output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database. 
2. Check that the query result, stored as an object in the output parameter, is not displayed in the edit data set dialog.
